quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  87,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  87,1,( ae paighambar ) apne perwar-digaar jallel al shan ke naam ki tasbeeh karo
  87,2,jis ne ( ensaan ko ) banaya phir ( is ke aaza ko ) durustkiya
  87,3,aur jis ne ( is ka ) andaza t_hraya ( phir is ko ) rasta bataya
  87,4,aur jis ne charah ugaya
  87,5,phir is ko siyah rang ka kora kar diya
  87,6,hum tumhe parha den ge ke tum faramosh nah karo ge
  87,7,magar jo khuda chahay. woh khuli baat ko bhi jaanta hai aur chhupi ko bhi
  87,8,hum tum ko aasaan tareeqay ki tofeq den ge
  87,9,so jahan taq nasiyaat ( ke ) nafea ( honay ki umeed ) ho nasiyaat karte raho
  87,10,jo khauf rakhta hai woh to nasiyaat pakdae ga
  87,11,aur ( be khauf ) badbakht pehlu tehi kere ga
  87,12,jo ( qayamat ko ) barri ( taiz ) aag mein daakhil ho ga
  87,13,phir wahan nah marey ga aur nah jiye ga
  87,14,be shak woh morad ko poanch gaya jo pak howa
  87,15,aur apne perwar-digaar ke naam ka zikar karta raha aur namaz parhta raha
  87,16,magar tum log to duniya ki zindagi ko ikhtiyar karte ho
  87,17,halaank akhirat bohat behtar aur paindah tar hai
  87,18,yeh baat pehlay shifon mein ( marqoom ) hai
  87,19,( yani ) ibrahim aur moose ke shifon mein
